news.title: Patna: Slow progress in linking land records to Aadhar despite May 31 deadline
news.para: According to sources in the revenue and land reforms dept, only 17.45 lakh people have so far applied for Aadhaar seedings and around 13 lakh applications have already been processed in the district.

news.title: Hero Realty to invest Rs 3,000 crore in residential project in Gurugram
news.para: The company, backed by Sunil Kant Munjal's Hero Enterprise, had formed a joint venture with Gurugram-based Saheb Enterprise to develop a premium residential complex in Sector 104, Gurugram.

news.title: Uttar Pradesh to transform 57 municipalities into smart cities with Rs 40,000 crore investment
news.para: The department has already developed 17 smart cities in line with this vision. The government allocated a budget of ₹40,000 crore for this project, with ₹145 crore already sanctioned as initial funding.
